ot skip it)\n\n### Coverage\n\n- `session-manager.ts`: 100% (statements, branches, functions, lines)\n- Overall: 96.64% (above 90% target)\n- All 155 files above 80% per-file floor\n\n### Verdict\n\n**Changes Requested** — 4 MEDIUM issues found and fixed. Story moved to `verifying`."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":321,"cache_read_input_tokens":45770,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":321,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01N6moxj4qqjLtwBuA4vgPGH","session_id":"45fbbef5-e9ca-4512-91b9-2760b179ad44","uuid":"0fcb9c22-8543-4409-8709-c27643ccdcc9"}
