{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_012ffYD1PrYd4JkvR3NcBg3z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012bzqfgSpfGrseU9dPMW7R9","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","content":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-04-02 (Session 10)\n\n### 4-1-agent-dispatch-module-sdk-integration — verification (2026-04-02T20:00)\n\n- **codeharness verify precondition failures**: The `codeharness verify` command failed with \"tests_passed is false\" and \"coverage_met is false\" because sprint-state.json caches stale test/coverage results. Actual live test run (27 passed, 100% stmt coverage) confirms ACs.\n- **AGENTS.md stale**: codeharness verify flagged missing entries for agent-dispatch.ts and agent-resolver.ts in AGENTS.md. Documentation gap, not an AC.\n- **bare:true mapping**: Implementation maps bare:true to permissionMode: 'bypassPermissions' + allowDangerouslySkipPermissions: true. Correct per SDK API but not 1:1 with AC wording.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 12\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 3, Grep: 1, Write: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: vitest full suite (~40 lines), vitest coverage (~50 lines), ls verification (~100 lines)\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: 3 bash calls to extract coverage due to truncated filename in coverage table\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — create-story (2026-04-02T20:04)\n\n- **Risks:** All ACs are test-provable (in-memory state objects), but true end-to-end session boundary behavior only testable at integration level in story 5-1.\n- **Observations:** Story 4-1 already implemented resume passthrough, so 4-2's scope is narrower than epic text suggests.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 13\n- By tool: Read: 8, Glob: 3, Grep: 1, Bash: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 11 unique, 11 total reads\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — dev-story (2026-04-02T20:09)\n\nNone.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 16\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 8, Edit: 3, Write: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: vitest full suite (~450 lines), vitest coverage (~150 lines)\n- Files read: 8 unique, 9 total reads\n\n### 4-2-session-boundary-management — code-review (2026-04-02T20:13)\n\n**Bugs found and fixed:**\n- MEDIUM: `resolveSessionId` — unknown boundary value fell through to `continue` behavior (should default to `fresh`). Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: `recordSessionId` — no validation on empty `sessionId`. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: `getLastSessionId` — falsy check conflated empty string with undefined. Fixed.\n- MEDIUM: Misleading docstring on `recordSessionId`. Fixed.\n\n**Architecture concerns:**\n- `recordSessionId` creates full TaskCheckpoint entries including `completed_at`. Story 5-1 workflow engine may also create checkpoints, risking duplicates.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 18\n- By tool: Bash: 5, Read: 8, Edit: 7, Grep: 2, Glob: 2, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: coverage run (~30 lines), git status (~25 lines), git diff (~14 lines)\n- Files read: 8 unique, 8 total reads\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":530,"cache_read_input_tokens":61887,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":530},"output_tokens":72,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"45fbbef5-e9ca-4512-91b9-2760b179ad44","uuid":"e76bdf60-7765-4c78-bd5b-8cf020f6e7c9"}
